Open Eclipse
File>New>Project>JavaProject>GraphSurf2
Inside src of the project directory copy pga
Get libraries from hadoop and giraph
Add those to build path
Compile and Run


For local run:
Right click GraphSurf2>Project properties>Run/Debug settings>Select GraphSurf2>Edit>Arguments
-asm /home/hadoop/workspace/GraphSurf2/ass (output directory)
-k 27
-reads /home/hadoop/workspace/GraphSurf2/Data/ (input directory)
-insertlen 180
-minuniquecov 10
-maxuniquecov 30
-wiggle 15
-threads 5
-maxthreads 30
-maxfrontier 15
-runPregelMerge
-w 1
